/*
Features Overview
Feature	Details
Board rendering	True-color Unicode pieces, light/dark squares
Square highlighting	Cursor (yellow), selected (green), legal moves (light green), last move (olive), check (red)
Keyboard controls	Arrow keys or WASD/HJKL to move cursor
UCI engine	Spawns any UCI engine via fork/exec, full I/O piping
Engine info	Displays depth, score, and PV live
Move takeback	U undoes one full move-pair (human + engine)
PGN display	Live PGN with move numbers, +/# colored, scrollable
Time controls	14 presets: Bullet/Blitz/Rapid/Fixed/Infinite
Promotion	Interactive promotion piece selection
Game over	Detects checkmate, stalemate, 50-move rule
Controls In-Game
Key	Action
↑↓←→ or WASD	Move cursor
Enter / Space	Select piece / make move
U	Undo last move
F	Flip board
S	Stop engine thinking
N	New game (back to setup)
Q	Quit
PgUp/PgDn	Scroll PGN
Usage with Stockfish
# Install Stockfish via Homebrew
brew install stockfish

# Run and enter path at prompt:
/opt/homebrew/bin/stockfish
*/

